3D Printing Services

We offer custom 3D printing services for prototypes, models, and functional parts using high-quality materials.

Custom 3D Printing

Our 3D printing services use the latest technology to create high-quality prints for various applications:

  • Prototyping for product development
  • Custom models and figurines
  • Functional parts and components
  • Architectural models and displays
  • Educational tools and visual aids

We use a Creality Ender 3 S1 Pro for FDM printing and an Elegoo Saturn 2 for resin printing, allowing us to create both functional parts and highly detailed models.

About NosytLabs

Founded in 2025, NosytLabs is the portfolio site for NOSYT LLC, showcasing our technology projects and services. Our name represents our mission: Notable Opportunities Shape Your Tomorrow.

We develop web applications, create technology content on YouTube (@TycenYT) and Kick.com/Tycen, provide educational resources on passive income opportunities, and offer 3D printing services using our Creality and Elegoo printers.

Our Core Offerings

  • Custom web development with React, Astro, and modern frameworks
  • Technology content creation on YouTube and Kick.com
  • 3D printing services with Creality Ender 3 S1 Pro (FDM) and Elegoo Saturn 2 (resin)
  • Educational resources on passive income opportunities
  • Open-source GitHub projects and development tools
